OL,3,CDetectorists unearth up to 15,000
OL,4,CRoman coins in North Wales
OL,6,FA metal detectorist has uncovered what
OL,7,Farchaeologists believe could be one of
OL,8,Fthe largest Roman coin hoards ever
OL,9,Ffound in the UK, estimated to contain
OL,10,Fup to 15,000 coins.
OL,12,FDavid Moss, 36, from Cheshire, started
OL,13,Fmetal detecting more than 8 years ago.
OL,14,FHe made the extraordinary discovery in
OL,15,Fa rain-soaked field in North Wales,
OL,16,Fguided by his new detector, a birthday
OL,17,Fgift from his fiancee Maria.
