OL,3,CDetectorists unearth up to 15,000
OL,4,CRoman coins in North Wales
OL,6,FThe hoard, which is still being
OL,7,Fanalysed, is thought to date back
OL,8,Fnearly 2,000 years and was found in
OL,9,Ftwo separate clay vessels.
OL,11,FThe collection, weighing more than 60
OL,12,Fkilograms, has been transported to the
OL,13,FNational Museum Cardiff for expert
OL,14,Fanalysis and is expected to be
OL,15,Fdeclared Treasure under UK law.
