OL,3,CDetectorists unearth up to 15,000
OL,4,CRoman coins in North Wales
OL,6,FMr Moss has been researching the
OL,7,Ffields for years, convinced that more
OL,8,Fhistory lay hidden after he found a
OL,9,Fsmaller Roman hoard of around 3,000
OL,10,Fcoins in the same area in 2018 using a
OL,11,Fdifferent machine.
OL,13,FHe said: "Something always told me
OL,14,Fthere was more here," he explained.
OL,15,F"I've always had a feeling there was
OL,16,Fanother hoard waiting to be found."
