OL,3,CDetectorists unearth up to 15,000
OL,4,CRoman coins in North Wales
OL,6,FRemarkably, a few days later, Mr Moss
OL,7,Freturned to the area to dig in another
OL,8,Fflat area he suspected could have some
OL,9,Fmore coins. Yet again, they received
OL,10,Fanother signal and the pair uncovered
OL,11,Fthe edge of a second vessel lying
OL,12,Fclose beside the first.
OL,14,F"We couldn't believe it," he said.
OL,15,F"Two hoards in the same area, it was
OL,16,Fbeyond anything we could have
OL,17,Fimagined."
