OL,3,CDetectorists unearth up to 15,000
OL,4,CRoman coins in North Wales
OL,6,FArchaeologists are now studying the
OL,7,Fhoards and the surrounding site to
OL,8,Flearn more about this significant
OL,9,Fhistorical discovery.
OL,11,FAfter treasure has been found, a
OL,12,Fcoroner holds an inquest for official
OL,13,Frecord keeping and to determine what
OL,14,Fexactly has been found.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Museum Wales said
OL,17,Fthey cannot comment until the
OL,18,Fcoroner's inquest is complete.
